      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 5118,
        "name": "沉玉谷",
        "desc": "<p>伴随着轻柔的微风，馥郁的茶香再度飘遍璃月的高原。</p><p>「茗生此中石，玉泉流不歇。」清微淡远的芬芳与古时的玉玦歌一同拂过翘英庄的河川，直至熙来攘往的遗珑埠。南方雾气氤氲的山岭间，不知又隐藏着什么样的奇遇…</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/15/142453215/c3b05f550a4a993a64548c995c9ab98c_8667469311642788970.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 5102,
        "name": "仙人",
        "desc": "<p>仙人是一群生活在提瓦特的不朽之物，千年来一直保护着璃月的人们。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/03/09/288375639/acf8b3f376f436b47bd1c4911fb9fe4d_8502257663901947323.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 5083,
        "name": "浮锦",
        "desc": "<p>沉玉谷内的一个仙鲤。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/16/288375639/87ac671b11a51263e1e810e44048dda0_5184248058160267270.png",
        "displayStyle": "card"
      },
      {
        "type": "CustomEntry",
        "epId": 5085,
        "name": "灵渊",
        "desc": "<p>沉玉谷内的一个古老猊兽。</p>",
        "iconUrl": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/15/288375639/5b4231e4ced390bfd124db7badbc7e2a_48301118341260960.png",
